data.description: This property in a coveted area of Arlington is definitely a hidden jewel.  Nestled at the end of a quiet cul de sac on a .5 acre lot to gaze at while sitting on an amazing deck!  This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom boasts a beautiful open floor plan with so many cute upgrades that make it a must see.  Just a short walk from Lake Arlington as well as close to the RANGER Stadium!  This home will not last!  Come take a look!
